---
title: Seared Steak & Nectarine Salad with Feta, Pecans, and Shallot Vinaigrette
description: A quick flash in a hot pan transforms juicy nectarines from sweet to nearly candy-like. Tossed with perfectly seared steak and tangy feta, this salad is bound to become a part of your summer repertoire.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-steak-and-charred-nectarine-salad-5106d678.jpg
